-body"><div class="k2t-title-bar teacher-title-bar no-sidebar parallax" style="" data-stellar-background-ratio=&quot;0.5&quot;><div><div class="container k2t-wrap"><h1 class="main-title" style=""> Piergiorgio L. E. Uslenghi, PhD</h1><div class="main-excerpt" style=""> Distinguished Professor Emeritus</div></div></div></div><div class="k2t-content no-sidebar"><div class="k2t-wrap"><main class="k2t-main" role="main"><div id="main-col" class="post-174 post-k-teacher type-post-k-teacher status-publish has-post-thumbnail hentry k-teacher-category-core-faculty"><div class="k2t-row"><div class="teacher-entry-meta col-4"><div class="k2t-element-hover"><div class="teacher-thumbnail"> <img width="400" height="400" src="https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/uslenghi.jpg" class="attachment-thumb_500x500 size-thumb_500x500 wp-post-image" alt="Piergiorgio L. E. Uslenghi, PhD" srcset="https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/uslenghi.jpg 400w, https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/uslenghi-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/uslenghi-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/uslenghi-55x55.jpg 55w, https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/uslenghi-80x80.jpg 80w, https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/uslenghi-130x130.jpg 130w, https://www.ece.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/uslenghi-100x100.jpg 100w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /></div><div class="entry-meta-inner"><div class="entry_teacher_number"> <i class="fa fa-phone"></i><span class="teacher_phone_number">+1-312-996-6059</span></div><ul class="teacher_social"><li> <a target='_blank' href="mailto:uslenghi@uic.edu"> <i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>uslenghi@uic.edu </a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="teacher-entry-content col-8"><h3 class="h"><i class="zmdi zmdi-account"></i><span>Bio</span></h3><div class="content"><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12"><div class="vc_column-inner "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p><strong>Contact Information:</strong></p><blockquote><p>UIC Dept. of Electrical &amp; Computer Engineering, 1020 Sciences and Engineering Offices (SEO), 851 South Morgan St.(M/C 154) Chicago, IL 60607.</p></blockquote><blockquote><p><strong>Office: </strong>807 SEO</p></blockquote><blockquote><p><strong>Lab Website:</strong> <a href="http://andrewlab.engr.uic.edu/" target="_blank">Andrew Electromagnetics Laboratory</a></p></blockquote><blockquote><p><strong>Lab Location:</strong> ERF B17</p></blockquote><blockquote><p><a href="http://www.ece.uic.edu/~uslenghi/" target="_blank">View Full Profile</a></p></blockquote></div></div><div class="vc_tta-container" data-vc-action="collapseAll"><div class="vc_general vc_tta vc_tta-accordion vc_tta-color-mulled-wine vc_tta-style-outline vc_tta-shape-square vc_tta-spacing-5 vc_tta-controls-align-left vc_tta-o-all-clickable"><div class="vc_tta-panels-container"><div class="vc_tta-panels"><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1467213097823-4ddaae4d-6e00" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title vc_tta-controls-icon-position-left"><a href="#1467213097823-4ddaae4d-6e00" data-vc-accordion data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Qualifications</span><i class="vc_tta-controls-icon vc_tta-controls-icon-chevron"></i></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><blockquote><p> Ph.D. Physics University of Michigan, 1967</p></blockquote><blockquote><p> M.S. Physics University of Michigan, 1964</p></blockquote><blockquote><p> Dott. Ing. Electrical Engineering Polytechnic of Turin, Italy 1960</p></blockquote></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1467134288052-dcd5bd39-e74e" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title vc_tta-controls-icon-position-left"><a href="#1467134288052-dcd5bd39-e74e" data-vc-accordion data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Professional Achievements</span><i class="vc_tta-controls-icon vc_tta-controls-icon-chevron"></i></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><blockquote><p> Fellow, IEEE</p></blockquote><blockquote><p> First Editor-in-Chief of Antennas and Wireless Propagation Letters, a new web-based scientific publication, 01/01</p></blockquote><blockquote><p> Honored as a Distinguished Alumnus by the Polytechnic of Turin, Italy, 04/01</p></blockquote><blockquote><p> President of the IEEE Antennas and Propagation Society, 2001</p></blockquote><blockquote><p> Vice President of the IEEE Antennas and Propagation Society, 2000</p></blockquote></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1467134393108-ce944a2f-a963" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title vc_tta-controls-icon-position-left"><a href="#1467134393108-ce944a2f-a963" data-vc-accordion data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Research Interests</span><i class="vc_tta-controls-icon vc_tta-controls-icon-chevron"></i></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><blockquote><p> Electromagnetics</p></blockquote><blockquote><p> Scattering theory</p></blockquote><blockquote><p> Modern optics</p></blockquote><blockquote><p> Solid state</p></blockquote><blockquote><p> Applied mathematics</p></blockquote></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1467134756414-2eca5de6-48b3" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title vc_tta-controls-icon-position-left"><a href="#1467134756414-2eca5de6-48b3" data-vc-acco